description:
Tobias Capwell is an independent scholar, curator, an expert on arms and armor, as well as a historical advisor for movies and TV. 

Today he’s breaking down some of the customisable weapons and armor of Warhammer 40,000: Space Marine 2's multiplayer Operations and Eternal War modes. 

What does a historian think of the Tactical, Vanguard, Bulwark, Sniper, Heavy and Assault classes?

What inspirations can he find within the designs of the Imperium's wargear and the arsenals of the traitor Astartes? And just which 40k chapter is his favorite? 

00:00 - Intro
00:43 - Tactical
05:22 - Assault
06:43 - Vanguard
09:41 - Bulwark
15:06 - Sniper
16:25 - Heavy
